# attachedNodes

**Instance Property**

A read-only set that contains the nodes you attach to the audio engine.

## Declaration

```swift
var attachedNodes: Set<AVAudioNode> { get }
```

## Attaching and Detaching Audio Nodes

- **attach(_:)**: Attaches an audio node to the audio engine.
- **detach(_:)**: Detaches an audio node from the audio engine.
